{
  "name": "RevOps AI: ICP & Segmentation Analysis",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🎯 ICP & Segmentation Analysis\n\n**Purpose:** Build your ICP from evidence — actual closed-won data ranked by ACV, sales cycle, and retention.\n\n**Trigger:** Quarterly as part of GTM planning, or when win rates drop.\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Connect HubSpot credentials\n2. Connect Anthropic API key\n3. Adjust date range (default: 6 months)\n4. Add company properties relevant to your ICP",
        "height": 388,
        "width": 396,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "53d84032-641e-4781-815d-ab2662a6b2b3",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -176,
        -16
      ]
    },
